snippet.title: Damnview: Built from Nothing Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Despair, capitalism and the need of seeking for a better future. 

Damnview: Built from Nothing is a simulation sandbox about Western culture and social class differences, coming to PC & consoles in 2019.

Join us on Discord: discordapp.com/invite/rDrG9vv 

Twitter: @Brainwash_Gang @SindiecateArts
